text: Veselina Gencheva (born 26 May 1981) is a Bulgarian gymnast. She competed in five events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Bulgaria Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Sofia
